General.Name: E & M Computing Ltd
General.Description: E & M Computing Ltd. provides cloud, information systems, and data-center technologies in Israel. It offers a range of services, which include professional services, data, big-data, and analytics, hyperscale cloud, business continuity, cyber security, software, hosted IT, rack-scale systems, and data center technologies solutions, as well as networking, OEM, and outsourcing solutions. The company was incorporated in 1984 and is headquartered in Ramat Gan, Israel.
